Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:11.36,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5}Pike or shiel{\fsp5}d{\fnBohemian typewriter\fs49}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:15.65,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5}I don't want to lose, but I don't want to hurt anyone either
