Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:18.49,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5}I took it so I could confirm
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:18.49,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur2.5}te ni totte tashikameteta
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:20.49,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5}that there's definitely no going back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.49,0:02:20.49,OP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur2.5}kitto modorenain datte
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:26.08,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5}Whose side are you o{\fsp5}n{\fnBohemian typewriter\fs49}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:27.75,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.5}Don't want to know!
